		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>sleight of hand</label>
				<description>{PAWN_nameDef} favorite childhood amusements was visiting a suburban circus and his favorite circus act was bare hands juggling with enriched uranium! Of course, {PAWN_nameDef} never had uranium, but this did not prevent {PAWN_nameDef} from progresing skills in this direction!</description>
